\n                <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-12 mb-3\">\r\n                    <p class=\"col-heading\">10<span>+</span></p>\r\n                    <p class=\"col-sub\">YEARS IN BUSINESS</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-12 mb-3\">\r\n                    <p class=\"col-heading\">300<span>+</span></p>\r\n                    <p class=\"col-sub\">TECH PROFESSIONALS</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-12 mb-3\">\r\n                    <p class=\"col-heading\">1500<span>+</span></p>\r\n                    <p class=\"col-sub\">CUSTOMERS WORLDWIDE</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-12 mb-3\">\r\n                    <p class=\"col-heading\">7500<span>+</span></p>\r\n                    <p class=\"col-sub\">PROJECTS COMPLETED</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section class=\"sec-3 my-5 py-3\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"row mb-5 pb-5 d-flex justify-content-center\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-8 col-sm-12\">\r\n                    <p class=\"heading text-center mb-4\">About Us</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-center small text-muted \">\r\n                        StartUp Assistant has been designed and developed by a team of diverse professionals belonging to various backgrounds. The application has been designed keeping in-view the needs of business owners, marketers and aspiring entrepreneurs. StartUp Assistant offers a free Business AI Chat Assistant and a suite of tools, resources, and services. It guides users through the entrepreneurial journey, aiding in tasks from selecting a business name to subscribing to services like Branding, Marketing, and Web Development.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"heading text-center mt-5 mb-4\">Services</p>\r\n            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center\">\r\n                    <p class=\"heading\">Digital Marketing</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">\r\n                        StartUp Assistant also provides you access to expert Marketing services including SEO, SEM, PPC as well as campaign designs and Social Media Marketing strategy\r\n                    </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex justify-content-end\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/assets/img/sec3-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\">\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"row my-5\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex justify-content-start\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/assets/img/sec3-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center\">\r\n                    <p class=\"heading\">Web Development</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">\r\n                        Elevate the experience of your visitor by getting a website designed by StartUp Assistant. Start a WebDev Project and explore different options to choose from\r\n                    </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center\">\r\n                    <p class=\"heading\">App Development</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">\r\n                        Native Android/iOS/Windows apps, dynamic web solutions, versatile hybrids, games, e-commerce platforms, and marketing marketplaces through expert App Development\r\n                    </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex justify-content-end\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/assets/img/sec3-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\">\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section class=\"sec-4 my-5 py-5\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n          <p class=\"heading text-center mb-4\">Features\r\n          </p>\r\n          <div class=\"\">\r\n            <div class=\"slide\">\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"box\">\r\n                    <div class=\"w-auto\">\r\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/sec4-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p class=\"title\">Feasibility Calculator\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">Industry benchmarks and market data to generate a comprehensive feasibility report along with potential profitability and probable risks.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <hr/>\r\n                  </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"box\">\r\n                    <div class=\"w-auto\">\r\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/sec4-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p class=\"title\">BNT Generator\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">Brainstorm catchy and relevant business names and taglines based on target audience, industry and brand identity preferences.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <hr/>\r\n                  </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"box\">\r\n                    <div class=\"w-auto\">\r\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/sec4-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p class=\"title\">Biz Story Generator\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">Leverage the power of AI to create different Business Documents like Brand Story, Mission Statements, Company Bio as well as Pitch Decks.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <hr/>\r\n                  </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"box\">\r\n                    <div class=\"w-auto\">\r\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/sec4-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p class=\"title\">Ad Script Generator\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">This feature assists users in creating effective ad scripts for various marketing channels, such as social media, video platforms, and search engines.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <hr/>\r\n                  </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"box\">\r\n                    <div class=\"w-auto\">\r\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/sec4-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p class=\"title\">SMS Builder\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">Social Media Strategy Generator feature helps users develop a comprehensive social media strategy for their business, including content calendar, posting schedule, and performance tracking metrics\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <hr/>\r\n                  </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"box\">\r\n                    <div class=\"w-auto\">\r\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/sec4-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p class=\"title\">BSR Generator\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text\">Business Strategy Roadmap Generator feature helps users create a visual roadmap outlining their business strategy, including key milestones, timelines, and resource allocation.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <hr/>\r\n                  </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n    <section class=\"sec-5 my-5 py-5\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <p class=\"heading text-center mb-4\">Technologies</p>\r\n            <div class=\"tab-container row py-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-md-4 button-container\">\r\n                    <div class=\"nav-tabs mb-3 d-flex flex-row flex-md-column gap-4 border-0\" id=\"nav-tab\" role=\"tablist\">\r\n                        <button class=\"nav-link active border-0 bg-transparent\" id=\"nav-home-tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-target=\"#nav-home\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"nav-home\" aria-selected=\"true\">Web Development</button>\r\n                        <button class=\"nav-link border-0 bg-transparent\" id=\"nav-profile-tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-target=\"#nav-profile\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"nav-profile\" aria-selected=\"false\">App Development</button>\r\n                        <button class=\"nav-link border-0 bg-transparent\" id=\"nav-contact-tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-target=\"#nav-contact\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"nav-contact\" aria-selected=\"false\">Digital Marketing </button>\r\n                        <button class=\"nav-link border-0 bg-transparent\" id=\"nav-Design-tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-target=\"#nav-Design\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"nav-Design\" aria-selected=\"false\">Design</button>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-md-8\">\r\n                    <div class=\"tab-content p-3 border-0 bg-transparent\" id=\"nav-tabContent\">\r\n                        <div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\" id=\"nav-home\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelled